casebody.head_matter:
Neil GILLESPIE, petitioner,
v.
REVERSE MORTGAGE SOLUTIONS, et al.
No. 17-8689.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 25, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
